        final var minimumVersion = getMinimumSupportedVersion();
        if ( version.isBefore( minimumVersion.getMajor(), minimumVersion.getMinor(), minimumVersion.getMicro() ) ) {
            CORE_LOGGER.unsupportedDatabaseVersion( ... );  // WARN level log
        }
    }
}
```

The comparison is **WARN-only** (not an exception). It logs: *"The %s version for [%s] is no longer supported, hence certain features may not work properly. The minimum supported version is %s."*

